#chip 16F887
#option explicit


/*
           ------------PORTA---------------
    Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
    IO:    ----------------------------AN0--
    IO:    ---------------------------------

           ------------PORTB----------------
    Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
    IO:    ----------------------------SW---
    IO:    ---------------------------------

           ------------PORTC----------------
    Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
    IO:    ---------------------------------
    IO:    ---------------------------------

           ------------PORTD----------------
    Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
    IO:   -DS8-DS7-DS6-DS5-DS4-DS3-DS2-DS1--
    IO:    ---------------------------------

*/

Do

    PORTD.0 = 1
    Wait 50 ms
    PORTD.0 = 0
    Wait 50 ms

Loop

End